    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl154_LabelType\">You inspire slaves to fight for freedom with a rousing battle cry.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl154_LabelType\">Andoran</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl154_LabelType\">As a standard action, you may make a rallying cry with a DC 15 Perform (oratory) check. On a successful check, any unarmed ally within 30 feet who is able to hear you gains a +2 trait bonus on attack rolls with improvised weapons and unarmed strikes. This bonus lasts for 1 round per level.</span></p>",
